":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":38549,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2022\/12\/25\/tahajjud-awf\/","url_meta":{"origin":34843,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Tahajjud: Awf witnesses the Prophet\u2019s night prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 25, 2022","format":false,"excerpt":"Awf ibn Malik reported: I stood with the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, to pray at night. The Prophet began to recite Surat al-Baqarah and he would not pass by a verse of mercy but that he would ask for it, nor did he pass by\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":19596,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/07\/26\/qaf-al-qamar-salat-eid\/","url_meta":{"origin":34843,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Eid: Surat Qaf and al-Qamar recited in Eid prayers","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 26, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Waqid reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, would recite in the Eid prayers, \"Qaf, by the majestic Quran,\" (50:1) and, \"The Hour approaches and the moon is cleft asunder,\" (54:1). Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 891 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Muslim \u0639\u0646 \u0623\u0628\u064a \u0648\u064e\u0627\u0642\u0650\u062f\u064d \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u064a\u0652\u062b\u0650\u064a\u0651\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\